  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 375°F (190°C).",
    "Cook sausage in a skillet over medium-high heat, breaking into small pieces, until browned.",
    "Add onion and carrots to the skillet and cook until tender.",
    "Add sweet potato to the skillet and cook for 5 minutes.",
    "Add cozy spice mix, brown sugar, and diced tomatoes to the skillet and stir to combine.",
    "Transfer the mixture to a 9x13 inch baking dish.",
    "In a separate bowl, mix together bread, cheese, and milk.",
    "Pour the bread mixture over the sausage mixture in the baking dish.",
    "Bake for 25-30 minutes or until the top is golden brown.",
    "Serve hot."
